DB
PostgreSQL database. Uses standard RDMS features, but also uses JSON fields for "NOSQL" like behavior.

MESSENGER
Background workers that will handle async messages sent to MQ.
Each worker has limits on time, memory and number of messages.

CRON
Background worker that executes scheduled tasks.
Each task is a shell script mounted directly into the container cron volume.
